{"_id":"elmer","_rev":"4-97fae8532edebabc102169228ddb843c","name":"elmer","description":"Element helpers for Atom","dist-tags":{"latest":"0.1.0"},"versions":{"0.0.1":{"name":"elmer","version":"0.0.1","description":"Element helpers for Atom","main":"./lib/elmer","scripts":{"prepublish":"grunt clean lint coffee shell:update-atomdoc atomdoc","test":"grunt test"},"repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/atom/elmer.git"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/atom/elmer/issues"},"licenses":[{"type":"MIT","url":"http://github.com/atom/elmer/raw/master/LICENSE.md"}],"dependencies":{},"devDependencies":{"coffee-cache":"^0.2.0","coffee-script":"^1.7.0","grunt":"^0.4.1","grunt-atomdoc":"^1.0.0","grunt-cli":"^0.1.8","grunt-coffeelint":"^0.0.6","grunt-contrib-coffee":"^0.9.0","grunt-shell":"^0.2.2","jasmine-focused":"^1.0.4","rimraf":"^2.2.2","temp":"^0.6.0"},"gitHead":"e295494e1c6b927d0cf632f52cb46ed6baa7cc4d","homepage":"https://github.com/atom/elmer","_id":"elmer@0.0.1","_shasum":"82d3b33b62b2820445d51e7a09fb6a411c7c9aef","_from":".","_npmVersion":"1.4.23","_npmUser":{"name":"benogle","email":"ogle.ben@gmail.com"},"maintainers":[{"name":"benogle","email":"ogle.ben@gmail.com"}],"dist":{"shasum":"82d3b33b62b2820445d51e7a09fb6a411c7c9aef","tarball":"http://registry.npmjs.org/elmer/-/elmer-0.0.1.tgz"}},"0.1.0":{"name":"elmer","version":"0.1.0","description":"Element helpers for Atom","main":"./lib/elmer","scripts":{"prepublish":"grunt clean lint coffee","test":"grunt test"},"repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/atom/elmer.git"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/atom/elmer/issues"},"licenses":[{"type":"MIT","url":"http://github.com/atom/elmer/raw/master/LICENSE.md"}],"dependencies":{"Node-bind":"git://github.com/Polymer/NodeBind.git#0.4.2","observe-js":"git://github.com/Polymer/observe-js.git#0.4.2","polymer-expressions":"git://github.com/Polymer/polymer-expressions.git#0.4.2","TemplateBinding":"git://github.com/Polymer/TemplateBinding.git#0.4.2"},"devDependencies":{"coffee-cache":"^0.2.0","coffee-script":"^1.7.0","grunt":"^0.4.1","grunt-atomdoc":"^1.0.0","grunt-cli":"^0.1.8","grunt-coffeelint":"^0.0.6","grunt-contrib-coffee":"^0.9.0","grunt-shell":"^0.2.2","jasmine-focused":"^1.0.4","rimraf":"^2.2.2","temp":"^0.6.0"},"gitHead":"7776184747be4686738985174cae85c08f770566","homepage":"https://github.com/atom/elmer","_id":"elmer@0.1.0","_shasum":"b870f08c7466ed43847659bc50853b1eb44ee45c","_from":".","_npmVersion":"1.4.23","_npmUser":{"name":"benogle","email":"ogle.ben@gmail.com"},"maintainers":[{"name":"benogle","email":"ogle.ben@gmail.com"}],"dist":{"shasum":"b870f08c7466ed43847659bc50853b1eb44ee45c","tarball":"http://registry.npmjs.org/elmer/-/elmer-0.1.0.tgz"}}},"readme":"# elmer\n\nExperimental view system for atom. Uses [polymer](polymer-project.org) [template binding](https://github.com/Polymer/TemplateBinding) project.\n\nSee [template-explore](https://github.com/benogle/template-explore) for a usage example.\n\n## Basic Example\n\nModel:\n\n```coffee\nclass TemplateExploreModel\n  buttonMessage: 'Clicked'\n  buttonClicks: 0\n\n  clicked: -> @buttonClicks++\n```\n\nCustom element\n\n```coffee\n{registerElement} = require 'elmer'\n\nTemplateExploreModel = require './template-explore-model'\nTemplate = require '../templates/template-explore.html'\n\nmodule.exports =\nTemplateExploreElement = registerElement 'template-explore',\n  modelConstructor: TemplateExploreModel\n  createdCallback: ->\n    @appendChild(Template.clone())\n    @rootTemplate = @querySelector('template')\n    @classList.add 'tool-panel', 'panel-right', 'padded'\n\n    @addEventListener 'click', (e) =>\n      @model.clicked() if e.target.matches('button')\n\n  getModel: -> @model\n  setModel: (@model) ->\n    @rootTemplate.model = @model\n```\n\nHTML Template:\n\n```html\n<template bind=\"{{}}\">\n  <div>\n    {{ buttonMessage }}\n    {{ buttonClicks == 0 ? 'never' : buttonClicks }}\n    <button class=\"btn\">Click Me</button>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n```\n\nAdding your new model/view as a right panel:\n\n```coffee\n@model = new TemplateExploreModel\n@panel = atom.workspace.addRightPanel item: @model\n```\n","maintainers":[{"name":"benogle","email":"ogle.ben@gmail.com"}],"time":{"modified":"2014-10-30T21:19:24.837Z","created":"2014-10-28T18:15:56.653Z","0.0.1":"2014-10-28T18:15:56.653Z","0.1.0":"2014-10-30T21:19:24.837Z"},"homepage":"https://github.com/atom/elmer","repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/atom/elmer.git"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/atom/elmer/issues"},"readmeFilename":"README.md","_etag":"\"4-97fae8532edebabc102169228ddb843c\""}